Ibyago byo kwandura Coronavirus (COVID-19) bigaragaza ko hari ibintu bisa n'ibyo mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Igihugu cy'ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, bikaba byemeza ko nubwo icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri mu byiciro bitandukanye, kiri gutera imbere mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
U Rwanda rwatangiye kubona ko ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bikeneye kwitabwaho cyane cyane mu gihe hari umubare munini w'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho.
Ku wa 31 Ukuboza 2019, mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa habonetse icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane by'ubwonko bitazwi.
Ku itariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe Gukurikirana no Gukurikirana Indwara cyatangaje ko uyu muntu ari Coronavirus nshya ubu izwi nka Coronavirus 2 ya SARS-CoV-2.
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara y'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 yiswe indwara ya Coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, abagera kuri 80% by'abafite COVID-19 bafite indwara yoroheje, ni ukuvuga ubwandu bw'imiyoboro y'ubuhumekero ifite cyangwa idafite ubumuga bw'ibihaha, abenshi muri bo bakira.
Mu bantu bagera kuri 14%, COVID-19 ituma umuntu arwara cyane akeneye kujya mu bitaro, mu gihe abandi 6%, bagerwaho n'indwara ikomeye igasaba kwitabwaho cyane.
Urupfu rw'abarwayi bavurirwa mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 ni hafi 4%.
Muri iki cyigisho, twerekanye uko COVID-19 ikwirakwira muri buri gihugu cy'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/icyanya cy'ubukungu cy'u Burayi (UE/EEA) no mu Bwongereza (Ubwongereza), turagereranya n'uko byagenze mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
