Mu Ukuboza 2019, Coronavirus nshya 2019 (2019-nCoV) yatumye habaho icyorezo ubu cyiswe indwara ya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), kandi virusi yiswe Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
