Gusuzuma mu laboratoire indwara y'ubuhumekero ya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) na virusi ifitanye isano na yo SARS-CoV-2 birimo uburyo bwo gutahura virusi no gutahura antibodies zaturutse ku cyorezo.
Ubuzima bwa virusi mu bipimo byemejwe na RT-PCR, igaragaza RNA ya coronavirus.
Ubu bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu buryo bwihariye kugira ngo bushobore gutahura RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 gusa.
Ikoreshwa mu kwemeza ubwandu bushya cyane cyangwa bukora.
Kureba umubiri (serology) bishobora gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma no kugenzura abaturage.
Igerageza ry'umubiri rigaragaza umubare w'abantu banduye iyi ndwara, harimo abantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyane ku buryo batashoboraga kuvugwa cyangwa abantu badafite ibimenyetso.
Ibipimo by'ubwiyongere bw'abantu bapfa n'ubwiyongere bw'ubwirinzi bw'abantu bose bishobora gutangwa hakurikijwe ibipimo by'iki kibazo.
Kubera ko nta gihugu na kimwe cyigeze kigira ibipimo bifatika by'ubwandu bwa virusi mu baturage bacyo muri Werurwe 2020.
Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyarigeze kigerageza abantu barenga 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi hari itandukaniro rikomeye mu mubare w'ibizamini byakozwe muri buri gihugu.
