Genzura ibyago bya COVID-19 mu kazi
Igenzura ry'akaga ka COVID-19 mu kazi ni ugushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bwo kugenzura ibyago byo kwirinda icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Ibikorwa byo kugenzura ibyago bikwiye mu kazi bigenda bihinduka bitewe n'aho ukorera n'akazi, hashingiwe ku gupima ibyago by'ibimenyetso by'ibyago, uburemere bw'indwara mu baturage, n'ibyago by'abakozi ku giti cyabo bashobora guhura n'indwara ya COVID-19.
Dukurikije uko OSHA (Ubushobozi bw'Umurimo n'Ubuzima bw'Umurimo) yavuze, imirimo ifite ibyago byo kurwara cyane cyane, nta mishinga myinshi iba igamije guhura n'abantu n'abandi bakozi.
Imirimo ifite ibyago byo kugira ubwandu buciriritse ikubiyemo abantu bakenera guhura kenshi cyangwa cyane n'abantu badafite COVID-19 ikekwaho cyangwa izwiho, ariko bashobora kwandura kubera ko hari ubwandu bw'umuryango urimo kuboneka cyangwa se ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Ibyo bikubiyemo abakozi bagirana na rubanda rusange cyane cyane mu mashuri, ahantu ho gukorera abantu benshi cyane ndetse no mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'ubucuruzi.
Ibikorwa byo kugenzura ibyago muri iri tsinda, uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura, birimo guhumeka hakoreshejwe imashini zifasha cyane guhumeka, amadirishya y'isuku no gutanga ibikoresho byo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye mu gihe ahuriye n'umuntu urwaye COVID-19.
LOSHA ifata abakozi b'ubuzima n'abahamba bagaragarijwe abantu bafite COVID-19 bakekwaho cyangwa bazwiho ko bafite ibyago byinshi byo gushyirwa mu ndwara, ikabahindura ibyago byinshi cyane iyo bakoze ibikorwa by'ubuvuzi bw'umwuka cyangwa gufata cyangwa gukorakora ibipimo by'abantu bafite COVID-19 bakekwaho cyangwa bazwiho.
Ibikoresho by'ubugenzuzi bigenewe abakozi b'aba bakozi bigizwe n'ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga, urugero nk'ibyumba byo guhumeka bifite umuvuduko mubi n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bigenewe uwo murimo.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kuba bari kure kubera ko barwaye, bagomba kwita ku bandi cyangwa kubera ubwoba bw'ibishobora kubagiraho ingaruka.
Imikorere y'ubucuruzi ishobora guhinduka, haba ku bihereranye n'ibintu bifuza n'uburyo bwo kubikura (urugero nko kugura hanze y'amasaha y'ikirenga cyangwa gukoresha serivisi zo kohereza cyangwa guhaha).
Amaherezo, kohereza ibicuruzwa bivuye mu turere tw'isi twahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye za COVID-19 bishobora guhagarikwa.
