Nanone kandi, batanga ingero z'ibipimo bikenewe kugira ngo ibyo bintu biteze akaga, n'ingingo z'imimerere y'ivugurura ishobora guterwa n'indwara z'ibyorezo.
Ibitekerezo by'igihugu cyangwa by'akarere bishobora gushyirwa mu bikorwa mu rwego rwo gutegura no guhangana n'indwara zandura.
Intego zo guhangana n'icyorezo zirimo kugabanya ikwirakwira mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara, gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku bandi bantu bo mu nzego zabo z'ibikoresho.
Uburemere bw'indwara mu baturage aho uwo mushinga uri bufite ingaruka ku byo umuntu yasubiza.
Iterambere ry'imihindagurikire y'ibyago rituma habaho uburyo bukoreshwa mu rwego rw'ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi kugira ngo ingamba zo kugenzura ibyago zigende neza.
Iyo ibyago bya COVID-19 bidashobora gukurwaho, igenzura rikora neza cyane ni igenzura ry'ikoranabuhanga, rikurikirwa n' igenzura ry'ubuyobozi, ndetse n'ibikoresho byo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye.
Igerageza gukora ubushakashatsi ku bintu by'ikoranabuhanga mu gihe uri mu kazi, kugira ngo ugire icyo ukora.
Igerageza ry'ubuyobozi rigaragaza ko hari ibyo umuntu agomba gukora kugira ngo agire icyo ageraho.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku muntu (EPI) bifatwa ko bidafite akamaro kurusha ibipimo by'ikoranabuhanga n'ibikoranabuhanga, ariko bishobora gufasha mu kwirinda bimwe mu birango.
Uburyo bwose bwo gutunganya imyanda y'ubwonko bw'umubiri (EPI) bugomba gutorwa hakurikijwe ibyago byugarije umukozi, bukagenerwa neza uko bikenewe (urugero, udupfukamunwa tw'ubuhumekero), bugakoreshwa neza kandi budahoreka, bugasuzumwa buri gihe, bugakoreshwa neza kandi bugasimburwa uko bikenewe, bukagororwa neza, bukagezwa neza, bukagororwa cyangwa bukagororwa kugira ngo hatagira ubwandu.
Dukurikije ibivugwa na OSHA muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, imirimo ifite ibyago byo kurohama cyane ku kazi, nta mishinga myinshi ibaho mu kazi n'abandi bakozi.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura zigenewe ahantu hose ho gukora harimo gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi mu buryo buhambaye, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, gushyiraho amarangi y'ubuhumekero, harimo guhisha akanwa n'uruhu kugira ngo bakonje no gututumba, gutanga imyenda n'ibisasu, kwitegura gukora kure cyangwa amasaha y'akazi akurikizwa igihe bikenewe, guhagarika abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi no gukomeza gukora isuku n'isuku bisanzwe mu mikorere y'akazi.
Guhita utabona abantu bashobora kwandura no kubirinda ni intambwe y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi mu kazi.
