OMS itera inkunga abarwayi binjira mu byumba by'abategereje bitandukanye bitewe n'uko bakekwaho COVID-19. Usibye izindi PPI, OSHA itera inkunga abantu bakora munsi y'ibirenge 6 by'abarwayi bakekwaho cyangwa bazi ko bafite ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 n'abakora ingendo zituma habaho umwuka.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, udupfukamunwa two guhumeka twemewe na NIOSH cyangwa hejuru y'aho, tugomba gukoresha mu gihe hari gahunda yuzuye y'ubutabazi bwo guhumeka, irimo imyitozo, imyitozo n'imibonano y'ubuvuzi.
Izindi bwoko z'amasiki yo guhumeka zishobora gutuma umukozi arushaho kurindwa no kumererwa neza. OMS ntishyigikira ko umuntu ahumeka kuko COVID-19 ari indwara yo guhumeka aho kwandura mu mazi.
OMS itera inkunga gusa abakozi bakora ubushakashatsi ku irembo ry'inzu bambara agapfukamunwa k'ubuvuzi.
Ku bantu bakusanya ibipimo by'ubuhumekero, bakita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 cyangwa bakabatwara mu gihe nta buryo bwo gukora aerosols buhari, OMS itera inkunga ko bagira agapfukamunwa k'ubuvuzi, amakanzu y'ibirango cyangwa igishushanyo mbonera cy'amaso, ikanzu n'amagaranseti.
Iyo uburyo bw'ikoranabuhanga bufite aerosols, agapfukamunwa k'ubuvuzi kagomba gusimburwa n'agapfukamunwa k'ubuhumekero (N95) cyangwa FFP2.
