Mu cyumweru gishize, twabonye ko umwe mu bakozi bacu bo mu mujyi wa San Francisco ashobora kuba yaranduye COVID-19.
Icyakora, kubera ko twari twihanganye, twatumyeho itsinda ryo gusukura virusi kugira ngo dushobore gusukura ahantu hose mu biro byacu byo mu mugi wa San Francisco.
Bakoresheje umuti wa virusi wo mu bitaro kugira ngo bashobore kwangiza imyanya yose, ndetse n'icyumba cy'inyuma n'igice cy'amababa y'amababa yazamutse igana ku igorofa ryacu.
Iyo nyubako ikoresha gahunda yayo yo gukora imirimo y'ubwitonzi ikoresha ibikoresho by'umutekano w'abacyubakira.
Twiringiye ko ibiro bizateguzwa neza igihe tuzaba dufata umwanzuro wo kugaruka.
Ibiro byacu byo mu mujyi wa Washington DC biri mu kigo cya WeWork, cyadusabye kandi n'abakozi bose bo mu mujyi wa Washington DC, ko bakoresha icyemezo cya COVID-19.
Kuva mu cyumweru gishize, ibiro byacu byo mu mujyi wa Washington DC byashyizeho uburyo bwo guhuza abantu kure cyane nk'uko inama za San Francisco zibiteganya.
Nk'uko bamwe mu bakozi bacu bo mu mujyi wa New York babizi, twaganiriye ku gitekerezo cyo gukodesha inzu i Brooklyn.
