Porogaramu za COVID-19 ni porogaramu zigendanwa zigenewe korohereza abantu guhura na Coronavirus 2019-20 icyorezo, ni ukuvuga kumenya abantu ( contact ) bashobora kuba bahuriyeho n'umuntu wanduye.
Hari andi ma porogaramu yagiye aterwa imbere cyangwa agatangwa, ashyigikiwe na leta mu turere tumwe na tumwe no mu turere tumwe na tumwe.
Ibikorwaremezo byinshi byateguwe ku bihereranye no gukora porogaramu zo gukurikirana imishyikirano.
Izo gahunda, cyane cyane izo zishingira ku gukurikirana aho abakoresha porogaramu bari, zituma havuka ibibazo by'ibanga ku bucuti bw'ibanga.
Hariho andi mahitamo atarakomeye cyane, harimo gukoresha ibimenyetso bya Bluetooth kugira ngo umuntu abone uko yegera telefoni z'abandi.
Ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje byombi ko hari uburyo bwo gushyigikira izi porogaramu za Bluetooth buzajya buboneka mu buryo butaziguye mu bikoresho byabo bya Android na iOS.
Leta y'u Bushinwa ifatanyije na Alipay, yatangije porogaramu mu Bushinwa ituma abaturage bashobora kureba niba bahuye n'abantu bafite COVID-19.
Ikoreshwa mu mijyi irenga 200 yo mu Bushinwa, naho Singapore yahisemo porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether.
Byatangiriyeho gukorwa n'umuryango w'abahanga mu by'ikoranabuhanga, byatanzwe mu buryo bw'isoko rusange kandi bizashyikirizwa guverinoma.
Iri koranabuhanga ryatewe imbere n'ibiro by'ubucuruzi n'ikoranabuhanga na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Kuva ku itariki ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu yari itegereje kwemerwa na Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku itariki ya 12 Mata, Guverinoma yavuze ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abagenzi iri mu cyiciro cyambere cy'iterambere kandi ishobora gutangwa mu byumweru bizaza.
Australia na New Zealand biteganya gushyiraho porogaramu z'ikoranabuhanga rya TraceTogether muri Singapore, zishingiye ku protocole ya BlueTrace. Uburusiya bushaka gushyiraho porogaramu yo kuvura ubutaka ku barwayi basanze bafite icyorezo cya COVID-19 baba i Moscow, kugira ngo birinde kuva mu ngo zabo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu mu by'ubuhanga mu by'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yavuze ibibazo byinshi by'ingirakamaro bishobora kuvuka mu gukoresha sisitemu zishingiye ku porogaramu, harimo ibinyoma byemeza ko ari byiza kandi ko bishobora kuba bidafite akamaro mu gihe igice gito cy'abaturage gusa ari cyo gikoresha porogaramu.
Mu gusubiza impungenge ku gukwirakwira kw'ibikoresho bya coronavirus by'ibinyoma cyangwa byangiza, Apple yemerera gusa ibigo byemewe cyangwa byemewe by'ibanze kongeramo porogaramu zifitanye isano na coronavirus muri App Store.
Google na Amazon byashyizeho amategeko nk'ayo.
Abashyigikiye umutekano w'ibanga batangaje impungenge zabo ku ngaruka za porogaramu za Coronavirus kugenzura abantu benshi, cyane cyane ko bishobora gutuma ikoranabuhanga ryo kugenzura abantu ryatangiye guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus, iyo icyago kimaze guhinduka.
Amnesty International n'indi miryango isaga 100 yasohoye itangazo risaba ko hakorwa ubugenzuzi buke.
Izo nzego zashyizeho ibintu umunani bigomba kubahirizwa mu mishinga ya Leta:
