Gahunda yashyizweho na Google/Apple igamije guhangana n'ikibazo cy'uko igenzura rikomeza kubaho, mu gukuraho uburyo bwo gukurikirana sisitemu ikora ku bikoresho byabo igihe cyose bitarakenewe.
Hari ibihugu byakoresheje sisitemu yo gushakisha ahantu hakoreshejwe imbuga nkoranyambaga aho gukoresha porogaramu, bityo bikakuraho ko hakenewe ko umuntu yurura porogaramu kandi bikakuraho ubushobozi bwo kwirinda gukurikirana.
